  "instructions": [
    "Prepare the earthenware bowl by washing it with warm soapy water and drying it thoroughly.",
    "Arrange the mixed greens in the bottom of the bowl.",
    "Top the greens with sliced provola cheese, apple, and pear.",
    "Sprinkle chopped walnuts over the top of the fruit and cheese.",
    "Drizzle the balsamic vinegar and olive oil over the salad.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Melt the tempering chocolate in a double boiler or in the microwave in 30 second increments, stirring between each interval until smooth.",
    "Drizzle the melted chocolate over the salad.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
